    <h2>Admissions Portal</h2>
    <p>Register your child for the upcoming entrance examination. After submission, you will receive a unique <strong>Index Number</strong> for the exam.</p>
    <div style="background: #fef9e6; padding: 20px; border-radius: 28px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <form id="admissionForm">
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;">
